  ('optician-moex-01377', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '最常作為隱形眼鏡消毒用之過氧化氫溶液濃度為何？', '["0.03%", "0.3%", "3%", "30%"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "efead02933a4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f889fe1f73a6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109180", "c": "402", "s": "1508", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年專技人員高等考試建築師、32類科技師(含第二次食品技師)、大地工程技師考試分階段考試(第二階段考試)暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01378', 'optician', 'optician-moex-109-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '若硬式隱形鏡片後弧半徑（基弧）維持不變，鏡片直徑加大（0.5mm），下列何者正確？', '["染色型態（NaFlpatterns）中心，維持不變", "因包覆瞳孔，滑動變大", "因矢深（sagittaldepth）變深，滑動變小", "滑動維持不變"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:33+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "efead02933a4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f889fe1f73a6", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109180", "c": "402", "s": "1508", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年專技人員高等考試建築師、32類科技師(含第二次食品技師)、大地工程技師考試分階段考試(第二階段考試)暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL)
